message.content: cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.COMM, cs.SY - The paper deals with communication systems and networks, specifically focusing on the use of relay cooperation and integrated microwave and millimeter-wave dual-band communication in 5G. This falls under the scope of information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), multimedia (cs.MM), communication (cs.COMM), and systems and control (cs.SY).
